Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:58.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}啊 有些東西映入我們眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}きっと誰にも奪われないモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}一定沒有人能夠奪走它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}無意味じゃない　あの意圖が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}那並非毫無意義的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 那是便利店的垃圾箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正千萬別接近平和島靜雄這人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿靜的暴力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道理說不通三句談不攏 不好辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒告誡過你不許再來池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄 打架可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？池袋最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說還是那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:37.99,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}ああ朝日は昇る 水平線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:37.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}啊 旭日初升 越過水平線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:41.79,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}今　信じれば變わるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:41.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}此刻只要相信 就能改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:48.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}無意味じゃない　あの光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:48.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}那並非毫無意義的一線光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司突然說要炒了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還趕我出宿舍 太突然了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辭退金也不給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙食費 生活費也沒影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家還不幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 都怪國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是國家不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是借了錢來風流快活？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄荷妹妹和我是真心相愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這家店裡見到她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不知道手機號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們是有真愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這家店裡見到她？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不知道手機號碼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先聲明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fn微軟雅黑\1c&Hffffff&}{\1c&H0F3DC8&}國{\1c&HFFFFFF&}士無雙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:03:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說最近平和島靜雄好像鬧得很凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個穿著調酒師服的人吧？平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他本來就很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近又變本加厲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池袋現在亂得像戰場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我以前也見過他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個很可怕的人呢 平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不要憑道聽途說就下判斷比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀塞頓 你認識平和島靜雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…那條道上的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人人都被你打飛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還怎麼收錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是兩三天前就沒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種人真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傳聞中狩獵人類那幫傢伙幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怎麼有傷員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是砍人魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了 往那邊逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 池袋又變得多事起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是很臭 整座城市臭氣熏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 靜雄 托姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 塞蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 最近他心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄 青春期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那算叛逆期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印章？（音近）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是電影的主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽島幽平很活躍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…平和島幽先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當哥哥的很有面子吧 平和島靜雄先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 其實我是做這行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅有外表 演技也相當精湛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出道作叫什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 『吸血忍者卡密拉才藏』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我就覺得他將來能成大器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得動作戲也不用替身就出色完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有哥哥的指導呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天關於這個話題 請您務必談幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我一開始也不是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是和弟弟幽吵架的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因一些雞毛蒜皮的事發火的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬起冰箱想扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的 不許吃\N靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我想搬它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是不得不搬它而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我控制不住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火氣上來身體便不聽使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後每次都會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有所謂火災現場的蠻力（狗急跳牆）嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜雄同學肯定能整天使用這種力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腦會抑制力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為一旦超越極限 骨頭和肌肉就會受損
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是靜雄同學的大腦卻讓力量爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可謂是生命的奧秘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人瞠目結舌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你的身體讓我檢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼死了 疼死了啊 靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體細節我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}斷了 要斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是遏制不住怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}尺骨 尺骨 我的尺骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後破壞周圍的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的身體也隨之損毀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只明白這點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄了忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然做不到那一開始就沒必要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會搞壞身體？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體傷過許多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而每次都讓我變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按新羅的說法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是在不斷變強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是會受傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 要多喝牛奶長壯點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 你也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闖禍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 回過神來 我就已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家是個普通的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼心理陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我剛進來良的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開張紀念 優惠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到又能上同一所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺是命中注定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後身體情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 為了慶祝我們重逢替你檢查…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼至少抽點血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整晚不回家擔心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去找腦袋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上這麼說 不是上哪找了個相好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞爾堤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別若無其事地戳人心口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}塞爾堤 我給你介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}他是我朋友 叫平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該怎麼表達好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}靜雄 塞爾堤是跟我合住的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得這傢伙不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}或者說是將來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起煩心事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 那只跳蚤混賬也是在那時出現在我面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 折原臨也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是和我一個初中的折原臨也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}唔 其實不算什麼好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一眼我就看他不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}不如說相當惹人厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分啊 新羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 本以為能和你相處愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛 靜雄同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 很愉快對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見面當天 我就和臨也打得死去活來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要理由 只是看他不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 他身體結實得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…失策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊 臨也也在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你怎麼沒受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}{\fs40}以後的日子變得無比煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙的傢伙接連不斷地找上門幹架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想過安寧日子而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見鬼見鬼見鬼見鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩躁煩躁煩躁煩躁…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是臨也 是臨也在幕後指使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了這點後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨·也！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把他宰了就清靜了 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來良畢業後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 合身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋從事這活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳蚤和黑道上的人混在一起 不知幹什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之暫時平靜了一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂看見沒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是演員羽島幽平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小幽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調酒師服？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得工作別換太頻繁比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能一直幹下去 就買了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 我盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨·也！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被跳蚤混賬陷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他離開了池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很快被無罪釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沒能遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs40}（不要飲酒駕駛 和我的約定）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這不靜雄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆是我初中的學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫他回收債務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了就是當保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初我沒想接這活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也不用你勉強出手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在池袋只要聽到平和島靜雄的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒人敢反抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那時起小幽也開始變成了大忙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再也沒見過面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽平先生 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎的 感覺輕鬆了許多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是到現在我還跟著托姆干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還款期限？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太複雜我不懂哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是寬鬆教育嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 學校社會 都是他們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有心理陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了我們不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾吧大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔這也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 瞧這什麼打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是管家啦管家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個不知道靜雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他誰？名人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎管家先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗 我噴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給本小姐換一杯嗎 管家先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在池袋混居然不知道靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是寬鬆教育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢弄髒我衣服…弟弟送給我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我還是不喜歡暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強到能遏制住自己的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你說了後感覺一身輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直煩躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我聽到些傳聞 有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 不好意思
